data.description: Gorgeous move-in ready home complete with new A/C (2023) and a new roof (2021 with 30-year warranty)! Featuring a spacious design and large windows throughout, this beautifully bright atmosphere is the blank slate you have been searching for and more. The main floor offers two large living areas along with a huge eat-in kitchen fully equipped with all appliances and an oversized center island. An additional loft upstairs provides a functional flex space to suit any of your household's needs. Retreat to the generous master suite boasting a huge custom closet and luxurious en-suite bathroom with a large soaking tub where you can relax and recharge after a long day. You don't want to miss this one, schedule your showing today!
